{"tid":2508140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西經濟部長：中國人發明了武漢病毒　中國疫苗不如美國疫苗","createTime":"2021-04-28T13:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T14:13:47.000Z","uid":227801,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6655cecc2626dd7ca1c10aa03ef195f96a2af475","tid":2508140,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T13:44:01.000Z","msg":"巴西傳媒報道，巴西經濟部長格德斯（Paulo Guedes）4月27日在一場會議上宣稱「中國人發明了新冠病毒（invented the virus）」，他又指中國疫苗不如美國疫苗有效。報道指，格德斯當時不知道發言遭錄下並在網上直播，他之後要求撤下影片。<br />\n<br />\n格德斯在一場巴西衞生委員會的會議中宣稱「中國人發明了新冠病毒，他們的疫苗不如美國的有效，美國人在研究方面已投資100年。」他之後稱，輝瑞（Pfizer）疫苗比其他疫苗更好。<br />\n《環球報》指，格德斯當時並不知道會議遭錄下，並透過社交網站直播，在他得知後，他要求不要播放，在會議結束後，巴西衞生部把影片從社交網站撤下。<br />\n<br />\n雖然格德斯認為中國疫苗不如美國疫苗好，但他本人在3月27日接種中國科興（Sinovac）的新冠肺炎疫苗。<br />\n目前巴西尚未使用輝瑞疫苗，2020年8月，巴西政府沒有接受輝瑞提出在12月前交付7,000萬劑的報價，2021年3月宣布向輝瑞購買1億劑疫苗，分兩期交付至今年9月。<br />\n巴西自1月17日起展開全國的大規模接種疫苗計劃，約8成使用中國科興與巴西布坦坦研究所（Instituto Butantan）合作研發的疫苗，另外2成使用阿斯利康（AstraZeneca）疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nhk01<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=2d163985\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk</a><del><a href=\"http://01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/618402/%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BC%E6%98%8E%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F618402%2F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%259&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=9962dc46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/618402/%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BC%E6%98%8E%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%9</a></del>7%85%E6%AF%92-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%<del>E4%B8%8D%E5%A6%82%</del>E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97[/url]"},{"pid":"e5fc208acf9e41c66f9c03500976b417f76b04fa","tid":2508140,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T13:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他之後稱，輝瑞（Pfizer）疫苗比其他疫苗更好。</blockquote><br />\n巴西隻刷鞋狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇biontech嘅話pfizer出撚到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b97bdce4f3779a4359837795f2717ae5342a0e","tid":2508140,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T13:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a497af7ae0cea67792b62de3cf7812b3ea6ee7d","tid":2508140,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T13:57:51.000Z","msg":"人人都知<br />\n得左膠唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280c101ded3fb7b99f6b2fa0c3a81ec0b0d3bf82","tid":2508140,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T13:59:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊個製毒既 梗係識解毒"},{"pid":"dc2954d0c4ed423000d025a164a166a551e4ef74","tid":2508140,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:12:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db319bfccb28c10917e58a29e8f996cee41aef3f","tid":2508140,"uid":236003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:13:23.000Z","msg":"講事實有咩問題<br />\n偽善撚又要吠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780a345062cac9be7b53ca9c7520ec3aa59621eb","tid":2508140,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:13:47.000Z","msg":"片呢？"}]}